Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 12:03:59 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] ADD terminal visual mode so focused pane text can be
 copied accurately

The terminal UI tracks vim-style character, line, and block selections over the focused pane, copies selected text through OSC 52, and uses row-offset mapping so left-pane metadata rows and wrapped right-pane content render in linear time.
